ning-causal-inference/foundation-models-for-time-series/</guid><description>Pretraining and transfer paradigms for generalized time-series intelligence.</description></item><item><title>Tool Use, Planning, and Memory for LLM Agents</title><link>https://SurpriseQiD.github.io/knowledge/generative-ai/tool-use-planning-memory/</link><pubDate>Fri, 13 Mar 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://SurpriseQiD.github.io/knowledge/generative-ai/tool-use-planning-memory/</guid><description>Design principles for robust tool calling, planning loops, and memory policies.</description></item><item><title>VAR, SVAR, and Impulse Responses</title><link>https://SurpriseQiD.github.io/knowledge/machine-learning-causal-inference/var-svar-and-impulse-response/</link><pubDate>Fri, 13 Mar 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://SurpriseQiD.github.io/knowledge/machine-learning-causal-inference/var-svar-and-impulse-response/</guid><description>Multivariate dynamic interaction modeling for policy and macro analysis.</description></item><item><title>不完全信息博弈：贝叶斯纳什均衡与类型空间</title><link>https://SurpriseQiD.github.io/knowledge/game-theory/incomplete-information-bayesian-games/</link><pubDate>Fri, 13 Mar 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://SurpriseQiD.github.io/knowledge/game-theory/incomplete-information-bayesian-games/</guid><description>建立不完全信息博弈的Harsanyi类型空间框架，推导贝叶斯纳什均衡的分析方法，通过双边拍卖、信贷配给和贸易谈判等应用案例说明私有信息对均衡结果的深刻影响。</description></item><item><title>信号博弈：劳动力市场模型、精炼贝叶斯均衡与均衡选择</title><link>https://SurpriseQiD.github.io/knowledge/game-theory/signaling-games-spence-model/</link><pubDate>Fri, 13 Mar 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://SurpriseQiD.github.io/knowledge/game-theory/signaling-games-spence-model/</guid><description>系统建立信号博弈的分析框架与精炼贝叶斯均衡概念，深入推导Spence劳动力市场信号模型的分离均衡与混同均衡，讨论均衡精炼标准与信号传递的本质逻辑。</description></item><item><title>动态博弈与子博弈精炼：序贯理性与承诺问题</title><link>https://SurpriseQiD.github.io/knowledge/game-theory/dynamic-games-subgame-perfect/</link><pubDate>Fri, 13 Mar 2026 00:00:00 